{"tid":292693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[心事台] 有冇人已經習慣左唔開心既野會收埋俾自己？","createTime":"2017-06-21T14:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T02:43:26.000Z","uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5861637767aae3b05af8f3cecf9c05dc95cfcc5d","tid":292693,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"望住同學，朋友生活過得越來越好既同時，<br />\n自己無乜點改變過，仲係度原地踏步。<br />\n<br />\n唔開心既野，講左出黎好似都唔會開心番。<br />\n一個唔覺意，仲會搞到D Frd灰哂。<br />\n<br />\n咁算啦，講出黎為乜呢？<br />\n周圍講，周圍放負都唔會有乜幫助<br />\n反正問題都係要靠自己去解決架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f306757da1a24d0adf4aaffbe943f61c54821d","tid":292693,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"連登呢度三唔識七<br />\n有咩唔怕講喎<br />\n幫就未必幫到<br />\n不過就叫講咗圍下爐無咁凍囉"},{"pid":"9a0781760d81d22ba240f8c1baf691dffc269f11","tid":292693,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"343783e9c79bd52e2d1e4319d4ee50c2d9d2d075","tid":292693,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好收埋自己"},{"pid":"d144261f7bfdccbdf3443ccb0e8a7f9e2c82f91d","tid":292693,"uid":121153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"摺埋某部份既自己 練下瑜珈"},{"pid":"93f8057ce086f8e4265e23c949dd3577c5381fde","tid":292693,"uid":20031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n成日覺得就算講左出黎都唔會有人在意<br />\n咁講黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如自己摺埋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707de89d02b249a3e2da106786ec1d167c6ce5af","tid":292693,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日想收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSad到字都打錯埋<br />\n哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bde1209671958c2a397d137ca35e434afb0c2d","tid":292693,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同感<br />\n成日覺得就算講左出黎都唔會有人在意<br />\n咁講黎做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如自己摺埋算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係有人在意所以更加唔想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前同個女仔FD講起自已女朋友，<br />\n覺得段感情開始冇乜希望，越講越灰。<br />\n最後搞到佢都身同感受，Sad埋，<br />\n反思自已係咪應該同自己個男朋友行落去。<br />\n<br />\n本身Sad果個係我，點解係佢喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無啦啦搞到我要tum番佢開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7563d68a8856acfec3ed10e37392f30e60abad02","tid":292693,"uid":1285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我相信大部分人都係咁"},{"pid":"de0b052cb89db73c0d81c3f514c806133e80f157","tid":292693,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a221c09c06885cccd0885413f5e3853f068b63dc","tid":292693,"uid":40257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"最慘係另一半都唔識開解自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有野寧願收埋都唔想曬口水講完換一隻哦字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10632f979b74f6cc3c057d0731028774be61eaac","tid":292693,"uid":20157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"講完出黎 仲要比人鬧番轉頭 <br />\n真係寧願收埋好過<br />\n忍下 過幾日就冇事架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}