bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲就話姐，<br />\n但我係巴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n性別一早定哂型啦。"},{"pid":"b35f054673d6dbfebfe1e2cc7a0a05e03c13481b","tid":292693,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"最近個人真係好撚累<br />\n心情好差,女朋友又分擔唔到..唉<br />\n好攰."},{"pid":"cd3fd7394860931b8304288483331a51032abb98","tid":292693,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講俾人知 自然有人氹翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲就話姐，<br />\n但我係巴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n性別一早定哂型啦。</blockquote><br />\n講俾另一半知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121b9fea83bd1fbe42fe5724b5af07c3c73cf678","tid":292693,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講完出黎 仲要比人鬧番轉頭 <br />\n真係寧願收埋好過<br />\n忍下 過幾日就冇事架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得講畀任何身邊嘅人聽都會無端端刺中神經⋯<br />\n唔講好過講。"},{"pid":"59cd96096492158ab0d8da8bd55500ccaa61341b","tid":292693,"uid":78549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"我成日都反省自己做過既野有冇影響到其他人同其他人對我既睇法<br />\n越諗越灰 好想搵人同我分擔<br />\n同fd講佢地就淨係識屌9我on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 我夠知我on9啦 唔on9就唔會後悔啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我只係想有人聽下我講野啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得唔需要畀意見我<br />\n只需要同我講我已經做得夠好同攬下我就夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係D人一係就屌9我<br />\n一係就喺度話我嗰陣點做先最好<br />\n一係就話我唔應該諗呢D野令自己唔開心<br />\n所以我所有野都收收埋埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14ea6b4c30cc76ff4436f38d708fa7a3a3fb1a6","tid":292693,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"係朋友面前係小丑<br />\n好少會同人講負面野 其實個人好負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多數都係做接收負能量嗰個"},{"pid":"525585c23eb55c81a4f6226e6fdab92cd9b2e1aa","tid":292693,"uid":34181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"今日又唔小心放左負，<br />\n唉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想咁多負能量阿。"}]}